<item>
            <title>[HBASE-5195] [Coprocessors] preGet hook does not allow overriding or wrapping filter on incoming Get</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5195</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Without the ability to wrap the internal Scan on the Get, we can&apos;t override (or protect, in the case of access control) Gets as we can Scans. The result is inconsistent behavior.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
